    "summary": "Helping you achieve your goals with creative translations that work\n\nI translate from English and French into Dutch and also edit existing Dutch texts and translations. My mission is to help my clients achieve their goals by providing them with an end product that is stylistically and idiomatically fully adapted to their target audience. The result is a translation that perfectly conveys the message of the source text but reads as if it had originally been written in Dutch.\n\nHaving worked as a professional translator for over 20 years, I have gained extensive experience in translating and adapting, among others, advertisements, manuals, brochures, newsletters, press releases and contracts for renowned companies operating in the advertising/marketing, automotive, transport, IT, medical/biological, law, insurance and tourism industries.\n\nAre you looking for a seasoned, reliable and accurate language expert who produces translations that work? Feel free to leave a message here or send me an e-mail at alberigs@planet.nl to discuss how I can help you.",
